cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.RO

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with visual object tracking and proposes a feature selection module to improve the performance of the tracker. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper uses Deep Convolutional Neural Networks (DCNN) for tracking and proposes a method to select more discriminative features. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with developing an intelligent system for visual object tracking. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with tracking objects in videos, which is a multimedia application. 
5. cs.RO (Robotics) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper proposes a method to improve the efficiency of the tracker, which can be useful in robotics applications.
